  BERND WIESBERGER:   Obviously happy, I got myself back into contention again and up the leaderboard, so very happy to see that, after a couple of hiccups, as well, during the round.   No, all in all, I like the way I hit the ball.   I like the way I executed my chances when I had them, so pleased with my game overall.  
   
 Q.   You were not entirely happy, because of the hiccups on the first day, but doesn't matter, if the hiccups keep producing this kind of score in the end?  
