 Q.   Not only up the leaderboard, but right at the top as things stand.   Is it going to stay come the end of the day?  
BERND WIESBERGER:   Yeah, got a couple of guys who really played well yesterday in the morning, and the conditions are still very good.   So I don't expect to be in the lead at the end of the day, but you know, there and about, and that's where you want to be on Sunday.  
   
 Q.   Very positive into the weekend?  
BERND WIESBERGER:   Definitely, playing nicely, quite in control, and I've holed a couple of long putts, but if I keep that momentum over the weekend, I'll be up there.   
   
  
  
  
  
  

